<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0,width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,date=no,address=no">
		<title>文档</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/api.css"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/aui.2.0.css"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/style.css"/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/swiper.min.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/iconfont.css" />
		<style>
			.aui-list:before {
				height: 0px;
			}
			.btn-box {
				width: 100%;
				background: #fff;
				height: 50px;
				text-align: center;
				padding-top: 10px;
			}
			.btn-box .aui-btn {
				width: 95%;
				padding: 5px;
				font-size: 1rem;
			}
			.fix-box {
				position: fixed;
				bottom: 0px;
			}
			/*详情*/
			.content-all {
				overflow: hidden;
				padding-bottom: 50px;
			}
			.content-top-box {
				display: -webkit-box;
				display: -webkit-flex;
				display: flex;
				-webkit-flex-flow: row;
				flex-flow: row;
				position: relative;
				padding: 10px;
				background: #fff;
			}
			.content-top-1 {
				width: 120px;
			}
			.content-top-1 img {
				width: 120px;
				padding-top: 10px;
			}
			.content-top-2 {
				-webkit-box-flex: 1;
				-webkit-flex: 1;
				flex: 1;
				padding-left: 5px;
			}
			.title-h1 {
				font-size: 0.875rem;
			}
			.span-img {
				border: 1px solid #BF6CF0;
				color: #BF6CF0;
				border-radius: 5px;
				padding: 2px;
			}
			.span-img img {
				width: 15px;
				vertical-align: middle;
			}
			.money-box {
				background: #fff;
				margin-top: 15px;
			}
			.money-box-top {
				display: table-cell;
				width: 1%;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
			}
			.money-box-top span {
				width: 48%;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
			}
			.money-box-top span b {
				color: #FF0000;
			}
			.money-box-bottom {
				overflow: hidden;
				margin-top: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.money-box-list {
				float: left;
				width: 22%;
				margin: 0px 5px 0px 5px;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 5px;
				padding: 5px;
			}
			.money-box-list.active-money {
				border: 1px solid #FF0000;
				color: #FF0000;
				background: url("../../image/zhifu1.png") bottom right no-repeat;
				background-size: 25px 25px;
			}
			.money-input {
				text-align: right;
				color: #ff0000 !important;
			}
			.tel-img {
				width: 35px;
			}
			.word-box {
				background: #fff;
				margin-top: 10px;
				padding: 10px;
			}
			.word-box h1 {
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				padding-bottom: 5px;
				margin-bottom: 5px;
			}
			.word-box p {
				line-height: 18px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="content-all">
			<div class="content-top-box">
				<div class="content-top-1">
					<img src="../../image/card5.jpg" />
				</div>
				<div class="content-top-2">
					<h1 class="title-h1">高速延长团购劵 92# 团购总升2千升团购可享91折</h1>
					<p>
						<span class="span-img"><img src="../../image/yz-ico3.jpg">已成团</span>
						<span>已售21000元</span>
					</p>
					<p>
						团购成功，不可退，未使用可转赠
					</p>
					<p>
						满<span class="red">1000升</span>可成团<span class="red"> 100升</span>起售 每人<span class="red">最高可购800升</span>
					</p>
					<p>
						活动截止日期：2016.12.31
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="money-box money-type-box">
				<div class="money-box-top aui-border-b aui-padded-l-10 aui-padded-r-10 aui-padded-t-15">
					<span>金额（元）</span>
					<span class="aui-text-right">
						<input class="money-input" type="number" />
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="money-box-bottom">
					<div class="money-box-list active-money">
						100
					</div>
					<div class="money-box-list">
						200
					</div>
					<div class="money-box-list">
						300
					</div>
					<div class="money-box-list">
						400
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="money-box-top aui-border-t aui-padded-l-10 aui-padded-r-10 aui-padded-t-15">
					<span>支付金额</span>
					<span class="aui-text-right"> <em class="red">200元</em> </span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<ul class="aui-list aui-margin-t-15">
				<li class="aui-list-item aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
					<div class="aui-list-item-inner">
						<div class="aui-list-item-title ">
							适用油站 （离我最近）
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-item aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
					<div class="aui-list-item-inner">
						<div class="aui-list-item-title">
							曲江庙坡头油站     30.00km
							<br>
							<span style="color: #888">近西安唐城墙遗址公园</span>
						</div>
						<div class="aui-list-item-right"><img class="tel-img" src="../../image/tel-ico1.jpg">
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-item aui-list-item-arrow aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
					<div class="aui-list-item-inner">
						<div class="aui-list-item-title">
							全部门店信息
						</div>
						<div class="aui-list-item-right aui-font-size-16">
							共24站
						</div>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="word-box">
				<h1 class="aui-border-b">团购细则</h1>
				<p>
					1.有效期: 自购买日起12月内有效
				</p>
				<p>
					2.该团购券限延长加油合作站使用
				</p>
				<p>
					3.无需预约、不可退款、不设找零，可分次消费
				</p>
				<p>
					4.不允许散装买油
				</p>
				<p>
					5.团购券与优惠券不可叠加使用且优先使用团购券
				</p>
				<p>
					6.请根据可用油站选择购买
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="btn-box fix-box">
			<div class="aui-btn aui-btn-danger" >
				立即支付 1019.20元
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/aui-popup.js" ></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/jquery.min.js" ></script>
	<script>
		apiready = function() {
		}
		//打开详情
		function openContent() {
			api.openWin({
				name : 'grouporder-pay-head',
				url : 'grouporder-pay-head.html'
			});
		}

		//选择金钱
		$(".money-box-bottom div").click(function() {
			$(".money-box-bottom").children("div").removeClass("active-money")
			$(this).addClass("active-money")
			var moneyNumber = $.trim($(this).html());
			$(".money-input").val(moneyNumber)
		})
	</script>
</html>